; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the EXPR_GENERAL path in auto transactions.
; When an auto transaction has an 'eval' or 'expr' directive, it is
; evaluated for side effects (the result is discarded).

= /Expenses:Food/
    eval 1 + 1
    (Budget:Food)              -1.0

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-50.00  Assets:Cash
             $-50.00  Budget:Food
              $50.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
             $-50.00
end test
